This project contains a derivative model based on Google's PaliGemma 2,
which is part of the Gemma model family.

Gemma is provided under and subject to the Gemma Terms of Use found at
https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms

==========================================================================

1. Base Model
   - Model: google/paligemma2-3b-pt-224 (PaliGemma 2, 3B parameters)
   - Provider: Google
   - License: Gemma Terms of Use

2. Modifications
   This project includes the following modifications to the original model:
   - LoRA (Low-Rank Adaptation) fine-tuning on a custom eggplant disease
     recognition dataset (Kaggle: sujaykapadnis/eggplant-disease-recognition-dataset)
   - 4-bit quantization (QLoRA with NF4) for training on consumer GPUs
   - Constrained Decoding implementation for classification output (0-6)

